room_title: Escape room "The Path" by Puzzle Effect Denver in Denver
room_address: 11674 N Huron St, Suite 300 Northglenn, CO 80234
room_description: A prophecy foretells of travelers from distant lands who are destined to rise to prominence as great leaders. The Oracle has devised a challenge to test those which have come to prove themselves. You are given 60 minutes to pass the test and prove that you are one of the chosen few spoken of in the prophecy.
